quran[10]{c,v,t,f}:
  96,19,"Ngwamba! Mmwe ngasimunkunda jwalakwejo, nambo nsujuduji (kuswali) ni n’diŵandichisyeje (kwa Allah)."
  100,7,"Soni chisimu jwalakwe jukuŵichila umboni pa yalakweyo (kupitila mu itendo yakwe)."
  100,8,"Soni chisimu jwalakwe pakuchinonyela chipanje juŵele jwakupelenganya nnope."
  100,9,"Ana ngajukumanyilila pandema jaichikoposyedwa yaili m’malembe?"
  101,4,"Lyele ni lisiku (lya Kiyama) lyachachiŵa ŵandu (sakalaalii!) mpela mapuluputwa gakusapalala."
  101,5,"Nombe matumbi gachiŵa (nkuwululuka) mpela litonji lyetyosye mbele."
  101,6,"Sano mundu jwachiukasitope n'diingo wakwe (wa yambone, nikwepepala yakusakala). ",footnotes:1:[Nnole Ȃya ja {7:8} ni chilaaki chakwe.]
  102,1,"Kumpele chipaka kusonganganya (ya duniya mwampikisano kuleka ganisya ya Akhera)."
  102,2,"Mpaka nkwikanila kwaula ku malembe (n'di m'bwile)."
  102,3,"Ngwamba! Chinchiika kumanyilila."